<p>We invest a great deal of energy in cognitive skills. We don&#8217;t spend enough time on character skills.</p><p>That&#8217;s one of the key themes of <a href="http://adamgrant.net/hiddenpotential">Hidden Potential</a>. To help you gauge your character skills, I&#8217;ve created a quiz&#8212;it identifies a strength and an area for growth. You can take it <a href="https://adamgrant.net/quizzes/">here</a>.</p><p>In an upcoming post, I&#8217;ll share some interesting patterns from the results. In the meantime, I&#8217;d love to invite you to join me for the <a href="http://adamgrant.net/tour">book tour</a> this fall:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="http://adamgrant.net/tour" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb633bf65-a5f2-415f-ba47-018018babf71_1080x1080.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb633bf65-a5f2-415f-ba47-018018babf71_1080x1080.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb633bf65-a5f2-415f-ba47-018018babf71_1080x1080.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb633bf65-a5f2-415f-ba47-018018babf71_1080x1080.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb633bf65-a5f2-415f-ba47-018018babf71_1080x1080.png" width="728" height="728" dat